parameters: Thief Nora: What kind of person is the magician Lapis?

Magician Relm: Lapis is someone who was expelled from the
Magic Academy. It seems they were secretly conducting
various human experiments.

Magician Relm: I didn't believe it much, but if what I heard
from Doctor Lapis is true, then it might all be true.

Priestess Sophia: At the Demon-possessed Magician Orphanage
of Stone Rock, Lapis would scold the naughty children when
they came.

Thief Nora: Eek! I absolutely don't want to meet them...
Ugh...

Priestess Sophia: Nora-chan is rare, so Lapis might not let
her go... ufufu
Thief Nora: P-Please don't say scary things like that!

Magician Relm: I cannot forgive those who stop at nothing
for the sake of their research and become a threat to
others.
Priestess Sophia (So Relm-chan is saying that)
Thief Nora (Relm-san doesn't seem much different either...?)
Magician Relm: W-What is it!? I have a noble purpose!

Priestess Sophia: Since it has fallen beautifully, shall we
go soon?
Clea: Yes, let's explore inside the cave.
Clea: Everyone, why are you all here?

Stolge of Affection: It seems that there was no need for
reinforcements since the two of them were exceptional.

Simos of Fuchiya: Hey, Clea is causing trouble again... Is
that Agonia guy favoring her or something?

Celis of the Gale: Simos-san sure complains a lot... You've
gotten stronger again... Your aura feels completely
different from before.

Researcher Dokusa: So, did you find out the whereabouts of
the object!?

Mage Relm: It seems like I was turned into a statue by Lapis
and she said she sold me as a sculpture...

Researcher Dokusa: I see... The object... It's sad... Very
sad... But you all are safe!

Researcher Dokusa: I'm glad you're all safe. As candidates
for assistant number 3, please continue to do your best.
Mage Relm: Geez... What is that... Such a strange person.

Researcher Dokusa: I will definitely bring back the object.
Please continue to cooperate with me from now on. Thank you
very much.

Stolge of Affection: Of course, that's the plan. I'll try to
investigate the special sales route.

Stolge of Affection: At that time, please continue the
investigation.

Researcher Dokusa: I will definitely retrieve the two
assistants...
